1. Do not forget to set the following environment variables prior
   to running qmake and make:
   a. QTDIR (/usr/local/qt)
   b. QMAKESPEC ($QTDIR/mkspecs/freebsd-g++)
   c. LD_LIBRARY_PATH ($QTDIR/lib)
2. Building QtChess as a plugin:
   a. Follow the instructions in step 1
   b. Run qmake -o Makefile qtchess.[shared | static]-plugin.pro
